displayProperties.name: Throughput
displayProperties.description: Average rate in Bps over last 3 mins, refreshed every 1 min

displayProperties.name: Current Connections
displayProperties.description: Active connections counted at the last sample time, measured every 1 min

displayProperties.name: Requests
displayProperties.description: Avg number of Requests received per min over the last 3 mins, refreshed every 1 min

displayProperties.name: Errors
displayProperties.description: HTTP 4xx and 5xx error count over the last 1 min

displayProperties.name: Client TTFB
displayProperties.description: The avg time for last few Reqs from Client sending first byte of req to receiving first byte of response

displayProperties.name: Locations
displayProperties.description: Number of requests distributed over the geographic area

displayProperties.name: OS
displayProperties.description: Number of requests distributed over OS type

displayProperties.name: Device
displayProperties.description: Number of requests distributed by type of devices

displayProperties.name: Browsers
displayProperties.description: Total requests distributed by type of browser

displayProperties.name: TOP CLIENTS
displayProperties.description: Number of requests distributed by client IP

seriesArr.name: Latency
seriesArr.formula: backend_time_to_first_byte /  ( status_2xx + status_3xx + status_4xx + status_5xx + status_6xx )
